```plantuml
@startuml castle-finance_vault-transaction-indexer
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor "Solscan API"

rectangle "AWS CDK" {
}

rectangle "AWS" {
  rectangle "EventBridge" as EventBridge #lightyellow
  rectangle "SNS Topic\nTransaction Hashes" as SNSTopic #lightblue
  rectangle "SQS Queue\nRaw Transactions" as SQSQueue #lightblue
  rectangle "DynamoDB Table\nRaw Transactions" as RawDDB #lightgreen
  rectangle "DynamoDB Table\nNormalized Transactions" as NormDDB #lightgreen
  
  rectangle "Lambda Functions" {
    rectangle "Index Transaction IDs" as IndexLambda #orange
    rectangle "Download Raw Transaction" as DownloadLambda #orange
    rectangle "Normalize Raw Transaction" as NormalizeLambda #orange
  }
}

EventBridge --> IndexLambda : Schedule

IndexLambda --> Solscan API : Fetch Transaction IDs
IndexLambda --> SNSTopic : Publish Transaction ID

SNSTopic --> SQSQueue
SQSQueue --> DownloadLambda
DownloadLambda --> Solscan API : Fetch Raw Transaction
DownloadLambda --> RawDDB : Store Raw Data

RawDDB -> NormalizeLambda : DynamoDB Stream
NormalizeLambda --> NormDDB : Store Normalized Data

NormDDB --> "External Analysis Tools" : Query for Analysis
@enduml
```